{"tid":220662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【C朗涉強姦】德媒：女事主直腸受傷","createTime":"2017-04-28T06:35:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T20:12:46.000Z","uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e0393df58aa30bdd2dd9e6136d33dbc8d7aa21de","tid":220662,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:35:41.000Z","msg":"德國《明鏡周刊》喺兩星期前爆料，指皇家馬德里球星基斯坦奴朗拿度（C朗）喺2009年夏天於美國拉斯維加斯強姦一名20歲女子蘇珊（化名），更令對方直腸受傷，最終以支付37.5萬美元（約292萬港元）掩口費了事。雖然C朗當時透過律師表示報道完全失實，純屬「傳媒創作嘅小說」，但《明鏡周刊》周四再度披露C朗喺2010年親筆簽署嘅庭外和解文件，顯示整份文件以「Topher」代表C朗。<br />\n<br />\n另外，該周刊亦聲稱擁有C朗同代表律師奧蘇里奧（Os&oacute;rio de Castro）嘅聯絡短訊，顯示C朗喺2010年得知被控後積極尋求庭外和解，當時對方開出95萬美元（約740萬港元）掩口費，C朗得知後大發雷霆表示費用過高，要求律師討價還價。"},{"pid":"fa0ccea5b3caf180481dabfe99f7ecbabcd26a1c","tid":220662,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:36:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170428/large/1493351029_b8b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170428%2Flarge%2F1493351029_b8b9.jpg&h=62fbdf20&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9926c375fe7ec40c74b0ab718ba26c8afde020b8","tid":220662,"uid":64225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:38:20.000Z","msg":"屌人直腸, 果然係基佬"},{"pid":"785d0f4c5830f55b2db7892663b17d0eb4eca5f8","tid":220662,"uid":1928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:40:26.000Z","msg":"強如c朗都要屌屎忽"},{"pid":"8433829d69e1ba934678f7b1cac0a5c4f0885e12","tid":220662,"uid":38173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:41:03.000Z","msg":"有錢就是任性"},{"pid":"ddcdc7d4aa8dbe434746617a2694c3c4e8a59d13","tid":220662,"uid":26266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3b321458830454b13f812ffe53f7bff66ae666","tid":220662,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor